=== LOST_ENGINEER ===
# id: 46
# title: The Lost Engineer
# chinese_title: 迷路工程师
# category: Crew
# mode: dungeon

A frazzled engineer stumbles out of a maintenance shaft, covered in grease and looking bewildered. He's been lost in the station's sub-levels for days, surviving on emergency rations. He offers his technical expertise in exchange for an escort to safety.

* [Escort him to the nearest safe zone]
  ~ gain_radical("车")
  "车" (chē) — vehicle, machine
* [Ask him to repair your equipment first]
  ~ gain_equipment
  "工" (gōng) — work, craft, engineering
* [Share your rations with him]
  ~ heal(10)
  "分" (fēn) — to share, to divide
* [Give him directions and move on]
  ~ gain_xp(10)
  "指" (zhǐ) — to point, to direct
